        "Target": "\u30BB\u30EB\u30EC\u30AE\u30AA\u30B9\uFF11\u982D\u3068\u30AC\u30E9\u30F3\u30B4\u30EB\u30E0\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Thousand Cuts, Totally Crushed",
        "Client": "Weapon Fanatic Guy",
        "Description": "Seregios cleaves with sharp\r\nblades, Garangolm crushes with\r\noverwhelming might! You see how\r\nawesome they are, right? They\u0027re\r\nlike a living sword and hammer!\r\nHow would a weapon specialist\r\nlike you handle them?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Seregios and a Garangolm",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Couper ou \u00E9craser ?",
        "Client": "Fana d\u0027armes",
        "Description": "Le Seregios tranche,\r\nle Garangolm \u00E9crase...\r\nCes monstres sont incroyables,\r\ntu ne trouves pas ? L\u0027incarnation\r\nd\u0027une \u00E9p\u00E9e et d\u0027un marteau...\r\n\u00C7a te dirait de t\u0027y attaquer ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Seregios\r\net un Garangolm",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Squarcia e schiaccia",
        "Client": "Fanatico di armi",
        "Description": "I Seregios squarciano con lame\r\naffilate, i Garangolm annientano\r\ncon enorme potenza. Splendido,\r\nnon \u00E8 vero? Sono come una spada\r\ne un martello viventi! Tu sai\r\ntutto sulle armi. Mi chiedo\r\ncome li affronteresti.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Seregios e un Garangolm",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Tausend Schnitte, Zerschmettert",
        "Client": "Waffennarr",
        "Description": "Seregios spaltet mit scharfen\r\nKlingen, Garangolm zerschmettert\r\nmit \u00FCberw\u00E4ltigender Macht!\r\nDu siehst ihre Herrlichkeit, oder?\r\nWie lebendes Schwert und Hammer!\r\nWie w\u00FCrde ein Waffenspezialist\r\nwie du mit ihnen umgehen?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Seregios und einen Garangolm.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Mil cortes y aplastamiento",
        "Client": "Loco por las armas",
        "Description": "El Seregios corta con afiladas\r\nhojas; el Garangolm aplasta\r\ncon poder devastador. \u00A1A que\r\nson algo alucinante! \u00A1Como una\r\nespada y martillo vivientes!\r\nT\u00FA que sabes de armas, \u00BFc\u00F3mo\r\nlidiar\u00EDas con ellos?",
        "Target": "Caza un Seregios y un Garangolm",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
